'''Al-Faatixa''' '''[[Suuratul Al-Faatixa]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Al-Fatiha; [[carabi]]: ﺳﻮﺭﺓﺍﻟﻔﺎﺗﺤﺔ; loogu dhawaaqo Sūrat al-Fātiḥah)<ref>"'''Al-Faatixa''' '''[[Suuratul Al-Faatixa]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Al-Fatiha; [[carabi]]: ﺳﻮﺭﺓﺍﻟﻔﺎﺗﺤﺔ; loogu dhawaaqo Sūrat al-Fātiḥah)"</ref> waa [[suurad]]a kowaad ee [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah ee [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka kaasi oo [[Alle]] (s.w.t) ku soo dejiyay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k.h). 

[[Suurad]]ani Al-Faatixa oo macnaheedu yahay ''fur-furid'', ''fur-furasho'' iyo ''bilaabid'' ayaa waxay ka kooban tahay [[aayad|todoba aayadood]] kuwaasi oo sharaxaya "mahadnaqa Alle", "naxariista Alle", cibaadada iyo ka cabsashada [[Ilaahay]]. Suurada al-Faatixa qof kasta oo [[muslim]] ah oo [[salaad]]a tukada waxaa ku waajib ah inuu akhriyo suuradan [[5|5ta jeer]] ee gudashada salaadaha faralka ah. Sida uu wariyey [[asxaabi]]ga [[Cabdullahi binu xudeyfa al sahamiyi|Cabdillahi ibnu Cabbaas]] iyo kuwo kaleba suurada Al-Faatixa waa mid [[Makki]] ah, taasi macnaheedu waa waxay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k,h) ku soo degtay asagoo jooga magaalada [[Makkah]].<ref>"Sida uu wariyey [[asxaabi]]ga [[Cabdullahi binu xudeyfa al sahamiyi|Cabdillahi ibnu Cabbaas]] iyo kuwo kaleba suurada Al-Faatixa waa mid [[Makki]] ah, taasi macnaheedu waa waxay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k,h) ku soo degtay asagoo jooga magaalada [[Makkah]]"</ref><ref>"Kitaabka [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah wuxuu ka kooban yahay [[boqol toban iyo afar Suuradood]] oo u sii kala baxa tiro badan oo [[aayad]]o ah"</ref>
